title: Wrong data set result returned when an invalid filter expression is set for row[0]
description: When a filter expression like 'row[0] equals to 0' is set, the data set result is incorrect or returns a null result set instead.
OB: The data set result is incorrect or returns a null result set when an invalid filter expression 'row[0] equals to 0' is set.
EB: A relevant error message should be displayed when an invalid filter expression 'row[0] equals to 0' is set.
SR: Display a meaningful error message when an invalid filter expression 'row[0] equals to 0' is set to help users identify and resolve the issue.
